<plot>A brillant singer is in love with a gifted composer but, during one of her performances, she collapses and a doctor warns her she must never sing again. Since her contract with the opera company specifies that the work of her lover/composer is part of the repertoire only if she sings, his work appears to be doomed.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?033580</url></doc>
